data.description: My advice to you is... Act Fast! Well taken care of 2 bedroom 1 bath home close to downtown, shopping, & dining. Picture yourself in a beautifully decorated family room with large windows your family will love and enjoy. There's no telling what you'll cook up in the perfectly suited kitchen-eating combo with range/oven, refrigerator, & granite countertops. Laundry room off kitchen area with washer & dryer to convey with property. Large fenced backyard with covered patio ideal to host family and friends. Pssst! Don't wait. Call to set a showing!
